<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870605-0106 </DOCNO><HL> Corrections andamp; Amplifications:Mattel Inc.</HL><DD> 06/05/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> MAT </IN><TEXT>   MATTEL INC., clarifying an earlier statement, said it plans to cut 300, or 14%, of the jobs at its corporate headquarters offices in Hawthorne, Calif., this year. An earlier edition suggested that the cuts were companywide.    (See: &quot;Mattel Will Pare 14% of Employees to Trim Overhead&quot; -- WSJ June 4, 1987) </TEXT></DOC>